<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Cloudflared Tunnel - iGreenMon</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
    <h2>New Tunnel Created</h2>
    <p>Hi,</p>
    <p>
      A temporary Cloudflared tunnel has been established.
    </p>
    <p style="margin: 1rem 0; color: #555">
      <strong>Temporary Access URL:</strong><br />
      <a href="<%= url %>" target="_blank" style="color: #1a73e8"><%= url %></a>
    </p>
    <p style="margin: 2rem 0; color: #555">
      Please note that this is an <em>ephemeral domain</em>. It will remain active only 
      while the tunnel is running, and may change if the connection is restarted. 
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 2rem">
      Kind regards,<br />
      The iGreenMon Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
